# Plot sizing and layout

## Sample plots


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
p_hist <- ggplot(mtcars, aes(x = mpg)) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 2)

p_text <- mtcars |>
  rownames_to_column() |>
  ggplot(aes(x = disp, y = mpg)) +
  geom_text_repel(aes(label = rowname)) +
  coord_cartesian(clip = "off")
```
:::


